## 6. Operations Manual

### 6.1 Daily Operations

**Morning Check (8 AM)**
```bash
# Check registry health
kubectl logs -l app=governance-registry -n indestructible-autoops --tail=50 | \
  grep -E "ERROR|CRITICAL|ALERT" || echo "All systems nominal"

# Verify evidence collection
curl -s http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/evidence/collection-status | \
  jq '.collection_rate'
# Expected: >= 99%

# Check hash chain integrity
curl -s http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/glcm/evc/chain-integrity | \
  jq '.integrity_percentage'
# Expected: >= 99.9%
```

**Evening Summary (5 PM)**
```bash
# Generate daily compliance report
curl -s http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/compliance/daily-report | \
  jq '.summary'

# Check for policy violations
curl -s http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/glcm/violations-today | \
  jq '.violation_count'

# Archive daily evidence
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/evidence/archive-daily \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d "{\"date\": \"$(date -u +%Y-%m-%d)\"}"
```

### 6.2 Weekly Operations

```bash
# Run comprehensive compliance audit
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/compliance/weekly-audit \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "frameworks": ["NIST_800_53", "ISO_27001", "SOC2", "GDPR", "HIPAA", "PCI_DSS"],
    "thoroughness": "COMPLETE"
  }'

# Generate component test coverage report
curl -s http://architecture-registry:8000/api/v1/components/test-coverage \
  | jq '.coverage_by_component'

# Verify all cross-registry mappings
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/validate/cross-registry \
  > weekly_validation_report.json
```

### 6.3 Monthly Operations

```bash
# Run full compliance certification audit
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/compliance/certification-audit \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "auditLevel": "COMPREHENSIVE",
    "generateCertification": true,
    "externalAuditor": true
  }'

# Update governance policies based on lessons learned
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/policies/update \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d @policy_updates.json

# Generate monthly performance report
curl -s http://execution-registry:8002/api/v1/reports/monthly-performance \
  | jq '.metrics'
```

### 6.4 Quarterly Operations

```bash
# Run full architecture assessment
curl -X POST http://architecture-registry:8000/api/v1/validate/comprehensive \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"depth": "COMPLETE", "includePerformance": true}'

# Execute quarterly compliance certification
curl -X POST http://governance-registry:8001/api/v1/compliance/quarterly-certification \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "includeThirdPartyAudit": true,
    "generateCertificates": true
  }'

# Review and potentially advance stage
curl -X POST http://execution-registry:8002/api/v1/stages/advancement-review \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d @stage_advancement_data.json
```

