## 8. Maintenance Schedule

### 8.1 Daily (15 minutes)

- [ ] Health check all registry services
- [ ] Review error logs for any CRITICAL/ALERT messages
- [ ] Verify evidence collection rate >= 99%
- [ ] Verify hash chain integrity >= 99.9%

### 8.2 Weekly (1 hour)

- [ ] Run comprehensive compliance audit
- [ ] Review component test coverage
- [ ] Update component test results
- [ ] Review and respond to compliance alerts

### 8.3 Monthly (4 hours)

- [ ] Full compliance certification audit
- [ ] Review and update governance policies
- [ ] Generate performance reports
- [ ] Evaluate stage advancement criteria
- [ ] Update documentation as needed

### 8.4 Quarterly (8 hours)

- [ ] Comprehensive architecture assessment
- [ ] Third-party compliance audit
- [ ] Generate compliance certification
- [ ] Stage advancement review
- [ ] Roadmap planning for next quarter

### 8.5 Annual (20 hours)

- [ ] Full system architecture review
- [ ] Compliance certification renewal
- [ ] Performance optimization analysis
- [ ] Security assessment and penetration testing
- [ ] Disaster recovery drill
- [ ] Team training and certification

